{"tid":1529731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肯定太子恐襲一定係有預謀，新屋嶺劇本，示威者責任","createTime":"2019-09-01T20:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T01:07:22.000Z","uid":110703,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f66bd354fbdc1e9a8e7f0be4f40283ad30f7863e","tid":1529731,"uid":110703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:14:42.000Z","msg":"Refer 另一個post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/724119284717359/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F724119284717359%2F&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=594205da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/724119284717359/</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇下佢地06:40班警幾淆!!!!!!淆咩??????</span></span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIau2kwxzZA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvIau2kwxzZA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=6283498c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIau2kwxzZA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇下4:40拎左擔架床!!!!!!!!究竟咩人要擔架床????係咪收埋左燃燒彈個個比你打到休克??????你唔比救護,急救員入去!最後訓床個個會點???????</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">------------------------------------------------</span><br />\n<br />\n想講少少關於831爆cctv睇法<br />\n當日夢到金鐘轉場果陣有少量手足<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽住 係少量！！！！</span></span><br />\n突然好撚燥喺月台見撚到啲cctv 就開始會棍打cctv 開頭唔成功 後尾再試終於爆咗一個半球體cctv<br />\n及後同一個人連續將其餘兩個或以上黑色長盒型cctv打爆<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">及後當我到咗尖咀 油麻地 旺角 太子 都見到cctv爆哂</span></span><br />\n點解講呢件事？<br />\n留意番上面6:40 正上方正正有一個cctv，已經爆咗，推極都唔會有片影到咩事<br />\n回想尋日蘋果live<br />\n當廢老打緊人，防暴狗已經滿佈 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係滿佈</span></span>旺角 太子站 根本就唔係打鬥而報警所致 諗下而家啲狗咁驚揾仔 唔會少數狗出 一出就大量 保障啲狗安全 求其報警話打交就有咁多防暴埋哂位 你信唔信？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">根本成件事係一個局</span></span><br />\n啲鬼一早爆哂，兼拉到其他人一齊爆cctv<br />\n諗真啲，cctv已爆，黨鐵肯交片都唔會有，因為已經<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">錄唔到</span></span>，俾示威者打爆仲可以spin去示威者到<br />\n加上好突發，算係raiding，月台記者唔多，有啲位出咗事，打人，死人苦無對證，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">成件事就係新屋嶺，不過喺黨鐵，兼spin落示威者到。</span></span><br />\n事後仲可以借啲以封站，慢慢作故仔，重拍案發經過。<br />\n<br />\n目的係震懾市民，製造白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n其實膠紙黐cctv好夠，狗一嚟<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即刻撕番膠紙。</span></span><br />\n至於閘機，售票機，增值機，隨便爆。"},{"pid":"699b1f8db519f9a96f82c2536e681dd0581ca907","tid":1529731,"uid":110703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:17:10.000Z","msg":"訓唔著幫推！1/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a3670bdb57398f4cb36714b35429b62a52301a","tid":1529731,"uid":110703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:17:27.000Z","msg":"訓唔著幫推！2/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548fc2cf475cdaf6736a5b2e4f7cc7b6df20ac4c","tid":1529731,"uid":110703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:17:39.000Z","msg":"訓唔著幫推！3/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1646c89990e952876f46da5a94e585f9d530ef","tid":1529731,"uid":110703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:18:03.000Z","msg":"訓唔著幫推！4/10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba12ffaa0b6b8875acbd6485d4734e4d635f0aa","tid":1529731,"uid":110703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:18:17.000Z","msg":"訓唔著幫推！5/10<br />